{
  "texts": [
    "As discussed earlier, students expected AI to serve not only as a writing assistant but also as a writing tutor.",
    "Nonetheless, a GenAI-assisted writing system lacks effectiveness without the ability to plan, initiate, lead, develop, and assess instruction in both domain-specific areas, such as writing, and in topic knowledge.",
    "It must also integrate content understanding with instruction.",
    "Without these capabilities, students may not gain a thorough understanding of the AI-provided content or how to blend it into their writing tasks.",
    "Furthermore, the system should create valuable learning opportunities and experiences."
  ]
}